{"tid":1998054,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"#TweetForTaiwan 國際線着晒火！撐台入世衛機會黎喇！","createTime":"2020-05-02T06:23:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-04T04:10:06.000Z","uid":255092,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3a5d9f48546405ae197fa6c2ce94bebad695cdf4","tid":1998054,"uid":255092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:23:41.000Z","msg":"<strong>【武漢肺炎】美發起#TweetForTaiwan運動助台入WHA  北京又再「堅決反對」</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200502/large/1588383618_63a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200502%2Flarge%2F1588383618_63a0.jpg&h=da6a8278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n台灣在防治武漢肺炎的成效，有目共睹，獲得國際社會高度認同。美國國務院國際組織事務局昨日在Twitter上發起#TweetForTaiwan（發Tweet挺台灣）運動，呼籲網民發文，將台灣「推進」將在本月底世衞大會（WHA）。多名美國官員、國會議員紛紛響應，不過行動卻引來中方不滿，中國常駐聯合國代表團表示「強烈不滿」和「堅決反對」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VUZBDj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VUZBDj&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=a3fc13a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VUZBDj</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>手足報恩既機會黎喇！<br />\n即刻上twitter retweet+like晒所有#TweetForTaiwan 既tweet！<br />\n係即刻！</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/TweetForTaiwan?src=hash\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FTweetForTaiwan%3Fsrc%3Dhash&d=eQX%2BqlmYp67lP1AM6ayufSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=5acbb10f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hashtag/TweetForTaiwan?src=hash</a>"},{"pid":"2dc20ad77d5d8d7e3a1bb885b1f9f966976b9e54","tid":1998054,"uid":255092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:24:20.000Z","msg":"光復香港！"},{"pid":"66ad2a796fd36550f6d2e92ad50222782a1f58b1","tid":1998054,"uid":255092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T06:24:41.000Z","msg":"台港同盟！"},{"pid":"502330fdbb5ff7dec78f1d78